<div class="container mx-auto mt-20 min-h-screen flex flex-col pb-24">
  <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">AI Chatbot</h1>
  <p class="text-center text-xs sm:text-base">旅について知りたいこと、不安なことはありませんか？</p>
  <p class="text-center text-xs sm:text-base">AI Chatbotに質問してみましょう！</p>

  <div class="card bg-blue-50 w-full sm:max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col justify-between shadow-xl rounded-lg p-6 mt-8 mb-4 flex-grow">
    <div class="card-body text-center flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-grow">
      <div id="chatbox" class="mt-4 w-full space-y-4 flex-grow">
        <div class="chat chat-start">
          <div class="chat-image avatar">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full">
              <%= image_tag "ai_bot.png", class: "w-10 h-10 rounded-full" %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="chat-header text-xs sm:text-base text-gray-500">
            AI chatbot
          </div>
          <div class="chat-bubble bg-green-200 max-w-xs mx-2 py-4 px-4 rounded-lg relative text-xs sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
            <p>こんにちは！私はAI Chatbotです。何か質問があればお気軽にどうぞ！</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-white p-4 pb-20">
      <%= form_with(model: @chatbot, url: chatbots_answer_path, data: { controller: "form-reset loading-spinner", action: "turbo:submit-end->form-reset#reset turbo:submit-start->loading-spinner#show turbo:submit-end->loading-spinner#hide", turbo_frame: "chatbot-form" }) do |f| %>
        <div class="form-group flex items-center space-x-4 w-full">
          <div class="mr-2 flex-grow flex items-center">
            <%= f.text_area :question, placeholder: "聞きたい内容を入力してください", class: "input input-bordered w-full h-16 rounded text-sm" %>
            <%= f.submit class: "hidden", data: { loading_spinner_target: "submitButton" } %>
            <button type="submit" class="p-0 pl-6 pr-0">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-8 h-8 hover:scale-110 transform transition-all">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 12 3.269 3.125A59.769 59.769 0 0 1 21.485 12 59.768 59.768 0 0 1 3.27 20.875L5.999 12Zm0 0h7.5" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
